<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/847354-is-this-the-same-as-hopeless-but-from-the">Is this the same as hopeless but from the guy point of view?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_847354'><a id="like_count_community_question_847354" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/847354?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F17340050-losing-hope">like</a></span>

