        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer532895057" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11196602186584477700">No one writes male P.O.V&apos;s like Colleen Hoover. No one. Losing Hope was utterly heartbreaking, compelling, and beautiful. And...I somehow managed to fall even harder for Holder than I already had in Hopeless.<br/><br/>Stunning.<br/>Stunning.<br/>Stunning.<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText11196602186584477700" style="display:none">No one writes male P.O.V's like Colleen Hoover. No one. Losing Hope was utterly heartbreaking, compelling, and beautiful. And...I somehow managed to fall even harder for Holder than I already had in Hopeless.<br /><br />Stunning.<br />Stunning.<br />Stunning.<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /></span>
