        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer895351284" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15646428830449340344">Well it wasn&apos;t the worst thing I read but it was not the best. I am not a fan of the &quot;same book, different person perspective&quot; ordeal. This just didn&apos;t feel necessary but okay</span>
  <span id="freeText15646428830449340344" style="display:none">Well it wasn't the worst thing I read but it was not the best. I am not a fan of the "same book, different person perspective" ordeal. This just didn't feel necessary but okay</span>
  <a data-text-id="15646428830449340344" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

